Refund Policy
<br>
If driver cancels > 72 hours of scheduled departure time then no compensations from the driver or app.  The app will help the rider find another ride if possible.
<br>
If driver cancels between 24 and 72 hours of scheduled departure time then the money paid by the rider can be used towards future travels on the app as a credit.
<br>
If driver cancels within 24 hours of scheduled departure time then the app will provide full refund and also arrange for another trip if available.  App will also provide a credit equivalent to the cost of the trip to use in the future.

